---
import MainLayout from '@/layouts/MainLayout.astro'
import Button from '@/components/Button.astro'
---

<MainLayout content={{ title: "Privacy Policy" }}>
  <div class="flex flex-col items-center space-y-8 pt-8 text-center">
    <h1 class="text-4xl text-black sm:text-6xl">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <h2 class="text-2xl text-gray-500 sm:text-3xl">Your privacy matters to Arian Architects.</h2>
    <div class="mt-4 flex flex-col items-center space-y-4 text-left max-w-2xl w-full">
      <p>
        Last updated: September 27, 2025
      </p>
      <p>
        At Arian Architects (“we”, “us”, or “our”), your privacy is a top priority. This Privacy Policy describes how we collect, use, and protect your information when you visit our website.
      </p>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-1">1. Information We Collect</h3>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4">
        <li><b>Personal Data:</b> Information you provide, such as your name, email, or contact details via forms or direct contact.</li>
        <li><b>Usage Data:</b> Details like IP address, browser type, and pages visited, automatically collected for analytics and security.</li>
        <li><b>Cookies:</b> We may use cookies for improved user experience and website analytics.</li>
      </ul>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-1">2. How We Use Your Information</h3>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4">
        <li>To operate, maintain, and enhance our website and services.</li>
        <li>To communicate with you and respond to your requests.</li>
        <li>To monitor usage and ensure security.</li>
      </ul>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-1">3. Sharing Your Information</h3>
      <p>
        We do <b>not</b> sell or trade your personal information. We only share data with third-party providers for essential services, bound by confidentiality, or when required by law.
      </p>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-1">4. Your Rights</h3>
      <p>
        You have the right to access, correct, or request deletion of your personal data. Contact us at <a href="mailto:arianarchitects@gmail.com" class="text-blue-500 underline">arianarchitects@gmail.com</a>.
      </p>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-1">5. Data Security</h3>
      <p>
        We use reasonable measures to protect your data, but no method is 100% secure.
      </p>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-1">6. Third-Party Links</h3>
      <p>
        Our site may include links to third-party sites. We are not responsible for their privacy practices.
      </p>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-1">7. Children's Privacy</h3>
      <p>
        Our site is not intended for children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.
      </p>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-1">8. Updates to This Policy</h3>
      <p>
        We may update this policy. Changes are effective upon posting to this page.
      </p>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-1">9. Contact Us</h3>
      <p>
        For any privacy-related concerns, please email us at <a href="mailto:arianarchitects@gmail.com" class="text-blue-500 underline">arianarchitects@gmail.com</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
    <Button href="mailto:arianarchitects@gmail.com" link={false} mode={true} text="Contact Us" />
  </div>
</MainLayout>
